                            <div><svg class="icon width-1 accent-icon" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 512 512"><path d="M173.898 439.404l-166.4-166.4c-9.997-9.997-9.997-26.206 0-36.204l36.203-36.204c9.997-9.998 26.207-9.998 36.204 0L192 312.69 432.095 72.596c9.997-9.997 26.207-9.997 36.204 0l36.203 36.204c9.997 9.997 9.997 26.206 0 36.204l-294.4 294.401c-9.998 9.997-26.207 9.997-36.204-.001z"/></svg></i>&nbsp;&nbsp;Restaurant&nbsp;&nbsp;</div>
